'''Caleb''' is a resident in a building that caught on fire.

==History==
Caleb was in his apartment when a fire broke out in his neighbor, [[Naomi|Naomi's]], apartment. When he realized where the fire was, Caleb tried to refuse to evacuate, but Theo was able to get him out of the building to safety.

==Relationships==
===Friendships===
He, [[Ivy]], and [[Naomi]] are friends. When Naomi wasn't answering her door after calling for help for a burn, he tried to refuse to evacuate without her.
